body: Closing this pull request in favor of a different solution, submitted separately.

Trafodion community: I won't be able to respond to issues for the next couple of weeks. If there are no major concerns with this change (that is, no regression failures and no reviewer comments pointing to serious issues), any committer can feel free to commit this in my absence. Otherwise, I'll respond to issues with reworks when I return.
